    <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl mb-6 leading-tight">Internet marketing services every small business should understand</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">Small business internet marketing works best when your website, local SEO, content marketing, social media marketing, PPC advertising, and follow-up systems all support the same goal: more qualified customers.</p>
