<article class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5">
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">Internet marketing services can sound broad, but most local businesses need a simple mix of visibility, trust, and conversion. You want people to find you, believe you are credible, and contact you without friction.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Start with local SEO</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">Local SEO helps your business show up when nearby customers search for what you offer. This includes your Google Business Profile, service pages, reviews, location content, and consistent business information across the web.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Use content marketing to answer real questions</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">Content marketing is not just posting for the sake of posting. It means creating pages, blogs, photos, videos, and social content that answer customer questions and prove your experience.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Add social media marketing for visibility and trust</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">Social media marketing keeps your business visible between searches. For small businesses, the best content is often simple: recent work, customer questions, promotions, team photos, and helpful tips.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Use PPC advertising when you need traffic faster</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">PPC advertising through Google Ads or Meta Ads can bring attention quickly, but it should point to a strong landing page or optimized profile. Paid clicks work better when the rest of your online presence already builds trust.</p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl mb-4">Build internet marketing strategies around one goal</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed mb-8">The best internet marketing strategies are not complicated. Decide whether you need more calls, quote requests, appointments, store visits, or online orders. Then choose internet marketing solutions that support that result.</p>
      <div class="rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 my-12" style="background:var(--primary-lt)">
        <h2 class="text-2xl mb-4" style="color:var(--primary-dk)">Quick checklist</h2>
        <ul class="checklist mb-0">
          <li>Optimize your Google Business Profile.</li>
          <li>Create a fast website with clear service pages.</li>
          <li>Publish useful content that answers buyer questions.</li>
          <li>Keep social media active and consistent.</li>
          <li>Use PPC advertising with a clear conversion path.</li>
        </ul>
